
---
import Layout from '../layouts/layouts.astro'
import Section from '../components/Section.astro'
---

<Layout title ="WEB SOLUTIONS UGANDA "
pageUrl="/"
>

  
  <div class="  md:bg-[url('/images/mobil2.jpg')] bg-[url('/images/Home1.jpg')] bg-cover overflow-hidden h-screen" >  

    <div class="text-white text- h-[100dvh]">

      <div class=" bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-60 h-[100%] flex justify-center items-center flex-col">
        <p class="md:text-5xl  sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-3xl font-bold text-white  pt-28">WEB SOLUTIONS UGANDA</p>
        <p class="md:text-4xl pt-2 md:font-thin text-xl font-bold  text-white  ">Grow Your Business Online</p>
      </div>
     
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<section class=" bg-gray-100 py-20">  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">We Build Websites That Work</h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
    <div class="service-card rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-200 p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">  <i class="fas fa-code text-5xl text-blue-500 mb-4"></i>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Website Design</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Create beautiful and user-friendly websites that capture attention.</p>
       </div>
    <div class="service-card rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-200 p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <i class="fas fa-rocket text-5xl text-teal-500 mb-4"></i>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Web Development</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Develop high-performing websites that meet your specific business needs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-200 p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <i class="fas fa-chart-line text-5xl text-green-500 mb-4"></i>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" >SEO Optimization</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Improve your website's ranking and reach a wider online audience.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center mt-5">
    <a href="/services" class="btn mt-7 px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-blue-500 text-white hover:bg-blue-700">See All Services</a>

  </div>
</div>
</section>


<section class="faq bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">Website vs. Web App: Know the Difference!</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
      <div class="faq-item rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-100 p-6 flex flex-col items-center">
        <i class="text-5xl text-blue-500 fas fa-file-alt mb-4"></i> <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Website</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">Imagine a beautiful online brochure. It displays information like text, pictures, and videos, but you can't really change anything. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-100 p-6 flex flex-col items-center">
        <i class="text-5xl text-teal-500 fas fa-code mb-4"></i> <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Web App</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">This is like an interactive online tool. You can use it to do specific things, like buying stuff online (e.g., shopping cart), checking your bank account, or even making appointments.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-10">
      <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Need Help Choosing?</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">No worries! Contact us, and we'll help you pick the perfect option for your needs.</p>
     <a href="/contact"><button class="btn mt-4 px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-blue-500 text-white hover:bg-blue-700">Contact Us</button></a>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



</Layout>


